OL,6, As weird and as plain screwed up as it 
OL,7, might seem, dear reader, I've always   
OL,8, felt a bizarre affinity towards the    
OL,9, technically still current ITV franchise
OL,10, holder for the South East, and not just
OL,11, owing to the fact that the South East  
OL,12, is where I live. I know, I know,       
OL,13, Meridian were no Granada in terms of   
OL,14, programme output, but my friends, what 
OL,15, a logo they had back in the day. What a
OL,16, logo indeed.                           
OL,18, Not a simple logo by any stretch, not  
OL,19, the sort of thing that would work as a 
OL,20, tiny app icon (as the 1999 ITV generic 
OL,21, look excruciatingly demonstrated), but 
OL,22, recognisable without a doubt.          
