OL,6, You may think that this is a bad thing,
OL,7, but I look back on those days fondly.  
OL,8, For a logo to have such a strong impact
OL,9, despite it only being on screen for a  
OL,10, few seconds is no mean feat.           
OL,12, In addition, I think children should be
OL,13, frightened more often by the TV that   
OL,14, they're spoon-fed, as it's good        
OL,15, character building and it worked in the
OL,16, 70s.                                   
OL,18, But having just seen Meridian's        
OL,19, inaugural broadcast, I now have an     
OL,20, unfortunate suspicion that the sunburst
OL,21, logo was the only good thing about     
OL,22, Meridian besides Dinenage and Thrower. 
